name: Camp Matress
description: The resting place of a former adventurer?

name: Camp Tent
description: An abandoned makeshift tent, who would have lived here?

name: Acid Larva Figurine
description: A lifelike representation of an Acid Larva.

name: Adder Stone
description: A porous smooth stone, some believe it wards off evil spirits.

name: Proficient Jewelry Workbench
description: An advanced workbench for creating rings and necklaces.

name: Alchemist's Table
description: Workbench to tinker with the wonders of chemistry.

name: Amber Chunk
description: Solid remains of an ancient forest. The light it reflects is warm and golden.

name: Amber Fish Egg
description: A perfectly preserved fish egg encapsulated in amber. How those two combined is a mystery.

name: Amber Larva
description: Grub encapsulated in amber, an extremely rare ingredient.

name: Ammonite
description: The petrified shell of an ancient sea creature.

name: Ammonite Necklace
description: Simple but beautiful necklace featuring a fossil.

name: Anchor Axe
description: This heavy weapon is actually just a ship anchor. Hits very hard and can throw enemies off.

name: Ancient Coin
description: Valuable ancient coin, currency of the underground.

name: Ancient Crate
description: A mysteriously glowing container holding ancient goods.

name: Ancient Feather
description: An unusual feather left by something big.

name: Ancient Gem Necklace
description: A necklace crafted with only using ancient gemstones as well as a super rare white version.

name: Ancient Gem Plate
description: This shimmering plate has intricate engravings, it looks like a key to something.

name: Ancient Gem Ring
description: This mysterious ring is entirely made out of ancient gemstones, featuring a super rare white one.

name: Ancient Guardian Necklace
description: A truly powerful relic of the past, made for fending off the strongest of foes.

name: Ancient Guardian Ring
description: A relic that is made in the same way as the Ancient Guardian Necklace, made for fending off the strongest of foes.

name: Ancient Hologram Pod
description: A strange device that materializes spirits of the past.

name: Ancient Pickaxe
description: Great architects of the lost civilization must have used this to take down almost any wall in their way.

name: Antique Board Game
description: An ancient game for two players, there is no rulebook but apparently it was about shifting blocks around.

name: Astral Jelly
description: Extremely rare type of jellyfish. It almost feels like out of this world.

name: Automation Table
description: Workbench for creating complex machines.

name: Azeos Beak Necklace
description: Forged from a piece of the sky titan's beak.

name: Azeos' Dash Feather
description: A colorful talon feather from Azeos, the Sky Titan. By holding it you can dash at a high speed.

name: Azeos Figurine
description: A lifelike representation of Azeos the Sky Titan.

name: Azure Feather Fish
description: A beautiful blue fish with scales that look like feathers.

name: Spicy Bait
description: A well-seasoned type of bait that attracts fish more quickly.

name: Green Bait
description: A pointy bait that can stick to fish from the outside to catch more and catch them faster.

name: Red Bait
description: A wiggly bait that looks like a red worm, quickly drawing fish closer to you before they bite.

name: Sticky Bait
description: An icky type of bait that pulls fish closer before they even bite.

name: Purple Bait
description: A shimmering bait that catches the eye of more rare fish.

name: Sweet Bait
description: A sugary type of bait that increases the chance of catching fish instead of loot.

name: Glowing Bait
description: A luminous type of bait that increases the chance of pulling up loot.

name: Expert Lure
description: This lure consists of multiple edible and magical components, attracting the one big catch that lingers in deep waters. Is consumed on successful use.

name: Balloon Spore
description: A fluffy giant spore. It's non-toxic but also not very useful.

name: Battle Axe
description: A menacing weapon that swings wide and hits hard.

name: Bed
description: A place to sleep. Also allows friendly inhabitants to move in if placed in a room to their liking.

name: Bent Fork
description: A simple fork that has seen too much use.

name: Stone tile "Cavelings"
description: A giant stone tile decorated with a deep blue glass. It depicts a gathering of cavelings.

name: Stone tile "Gemstone"
description: A giant stone tile decorated with a deep blue glass. It depicts a glowing gemstone.

name: Stone tile "Scholar"
description: A giant stone tile decorated with a deep blue glass. It depicts a robed caveling.

name: Big Larva Figurine
description: A lifelike representation of a Big Larva.

name: Blue Bikini Top
description: A blue swim suit piece that keeps everything in its place. Everyone knows the most revealing armor is the most protective.

name: Green Bikini Top
description: A green swim suit piece that keeps everything in its place. Everyone knows the most revealing armor is the most protective.

name: Red Bikini Top
description: A red swim suit piece that keeps everything in its place. Everyone knows the most revealing armor is the most protective.

name: Blue Bikini Bottom
description: A blue underwear piece that goes well with its top part. Get rid of unnecessary clothing and run free in the sun!

name: Green Bikini Bottom
description: A green underwear piece that goes well with its top part. Get rid of unnecessary clothing and run free in the sun!

name: Red Bikini Bottom
description: A red underwear piece that goes well with its top part. Get rid of unnecessary clothing and run free in the sun!

name: Azeos the Sky Titan Scanner
description: Scans the world for Azeos the Sky Titan. Consumed on successful scan.

name: Black Bubble Pearl
description: A black variant of the bubble pearl, from certain angles it appears golden.

name: Black Steel Urchin
description: A rare sea critter with spikes as hard as steel.

name: Bloat Oat
description: A handful of healthy cereal that fills you up and gives you energy.

name: Golden Bloat Oat
description: A very rare variant of the common bloat oat.

name: Bloat Oat Seed
description: Grows into a filling crop when planted.

name: Blob Rosary Necklace
description: Sticky necklace infused with energy made for an unknown purpose.

name: Blood Skull
description: The crimson remains of someone meeting a terrible fate.

name: Blowpipe
description: A simple weapon loaded with poisonous darts.

name: Blue Cave Guppy
description: Small, blue fish home to the dirt cave lakes.

name: Blue Kelp
description: A blue lump of marine plants, not that useful.

name: Blue Slime Figurine
description: A lifelike representation of a slippery Blue Slime.

name: Boat
description: Allows travelling over water.

name: Boat Workbench
description: This wide workstation allows the construction of different boats. Ahoy!

name: Bomb
description: A stronger explosive for crowd control and facing giant enemies.

name: Bomb Pepper
description: A fierce vegetable for spicing up foods.

name: Golden Bomb Pepper
description: A very rare variant of the common bomb pepper.

name: Bomb Pepper Seed
description: Grows into a spicy vegetable when planted.

name: Bone Creole
description: A crude piece of jewelry carved from bone.

name: Titan's Chest
description: A large, ancient chest crested with gemstones.

name: Bottom Tracer
description: A bright yellow fish with long barbels that it drags along the sea floor in search for food.

name: Broken Core Idol
description: A familiar-looking object.

name: Broken Handle
description: A piece of an ancient weapon. Even though it's only the handle it already feels mysteriously balanced in your hand.

name: Broken Stone Pillar
description: Unstable pillar for decoration, probably thousands of years old.

name: Bronze Breastplate
description: A good armor to survive battles more easily.

name: Bronze Helm
description: This helm repels slight blows to the head.

name: Bronze Pants
description: Some bronze for the shin.

name: Bubble Gun
description: A strange ranged weapon that shoots out hovering bubbles, adding slippery movement on contact.

name: Bubble Pearl
description: A beautiful, iridescent pearl. It seems to be hollow.

name: Bubble Pearl Necklace
description: Natural grown jewelry made from rare bubble pearls.

name: Bush
description: Stubby patch of grass to use as a decorative.

name: Campfire
description: Great for huddling together, telling stories and burning marshmallows to a crisp.

name: Carapace Breastplate
description: An organic body armor resembling Ghorm's shell, it is heavy and feels weird on the inside.

name: Carapace Helm
description: A chitin-plated head piece, wearing it fills you with the urge to dig paths through the darkness.

name: Carpenter's Table
description: Workbench for crafting decorative furnishing.

name: Carrock
description: Rock-hard vegetable that toughens you up.

name: Golden Carrock
description: A very rare variant of the common carrock.

name: Carrock Seed
description: A tough seed that only grows in stone.

name: Cartography Table
description: A table to share your map discoveries with other explorers.

name: Cave Guppy Necklace
description: Odd necklace made from a fish that never let go of the hook.

name: Cave Pouch
description: Every underground miner needs one of those!

name: Caveling Bed
description: Doesn't look very comfortable.

name: Caveling Bread
description: Dry, hard bread. It feels like chewing chalk but fills the stomach.

name: Caveling Chest
description: Made from grub leather, good for unhindered movement in combat.

name: Caveling Brute Figurine
description: A lifelike representation of a Caveling Brute.

name: Caveling Chair
description: A stool made from stone.

name: Cave Coffee
description: A strong, bottled brew made from unknown ingredients. After ingesting it's hard for you to stand still.

name: Cave Crunch
description: A chunky, sweet snack in a wrapper. Must be thousands of years old and probably still edible for a couple more.

name: Caveling Cup
description: This small drinking that cup must have held many different beverages. There is still a faint smell of something sweet.

name: Caveling Doll
description: A handmade doll found in a grave. It must once have belonged to a child...

name: Caveling Effigy
description: A small depiction of a caveling, it's hollow and must have been used for storing small goods.

name: Caveling Gardener Figurine
description: A lifelike representation of a Caveling Gardener.

name: Caveling Floor Tile
description: A crumbly stone slab with simple patterns embedded in it.

name: Dark Caveling Floor Tile
description: A dark version of the ancient floor tiles, it looks much older.

name: Caveling Hood
description: Light armor hood that hides the face.

name: Caveling Hunter Figurine
description: A lifelike representation of a Caveling Hunter.

name: Caveling ID
description: A sturdy card that once belonged to a citizen of the forlorn metropolis. It's thousand of years old but the excellent print hasn't faded.

name: Infected Caveling Figurine
description: A lifelike representation of a Infected Caveling.

name: Caveling Medal
description: Minted medallion with a face relief. Has it been awarded to someone extraordinary once?

name: Caveling Mother's Ring
description: An old crystal ring, holding it fills you with a sad feeling you can't describe.

name: Caveling Pants
description: These pants don't cover much but make your movement more elusive.

name: Caveling Perfume
description: A blue fragrance bottle. It is tightly sealed but emits a heavenly scent.

name: Caveling Pot
description: An urn made from stone filled with the belongings of cavelings.

name: Caveling Shaman Figurine
description: A lifelike representation of a Caveling Shaman.

name: Blue Leather Tome
description: An ancient book with stitched blue covers. Is that skin?

name: Caveling Skull
description: Remains of what was once a proud civilization.

name: Caveling Table
description: A crude, blocky piece of furniture, many meals must have been shared on it.

name: Caveling throne
description: This unusual seat is proof of an empire fallen to ruin.

name: Caveling Toilet
description: Between mining there must be time for serious business.

name: Caveling Figurine
description: A lifelike representation of a Caveling.

name: Ceremonial Flute
description: An ancient, precious instrument but it is clogged.

name: Chipped Plate
description: An old stone plate. What kind of food has been served on it?

name: Chrysalis
description: Icky groundcover that feels strange to walk across. Larvas will infest chrysalis-covered areas over time.

name: Urban Moss
description: Ground plants found in the forlorn metropolis. They grow tiny berries that attract cavelings of the corresponding area.

name: Metropolis Crate
description: This precious container holds useful items that have been used by citizens of the ancient city.

name: Clot Ring
description: A blood-red ring that latches onto your finger.

name: Cocoon Figurine
description: A lifelike representation of a cocoon.

name: Conch Shell Necklace
description: A beautiful necklace featuring a small shell. When you hold it up to your ear you can hear distant waves.

name: Conveyor Belt
description: Transport your resources!

name: Cooking Pot
description: Cooking ingredients brings out their full potential. Combine two and see what happens!

name: Copper Anvil
description: Get started with creating armor for looks and combat.

name: Copper Bar
description: A simple metal ingot for blacksmithing.

name: Copper Breastplate
description: Got no sixpack? Just craft one!

name: Copper Cross Necklace
description: This pendant sharpens the focus, allowing for more precise hits.

name: Copper Helm
description: Resembles more of a bucket but repels strong blows to the head.

name: Copper Hoe
description: A sturdy tool to prepare ground for farming.

name: Copper Pickaxe
description: A sturdy tool, well-suited for breaking down walls effortlessly.

name: Copper Pants
description: Protects the shins with ease.

name: Copper Shovel
description: A sturdy shovel, good for digging up ground.

name: Copper Sword
description: A good weapon for slaying foes.

name: Coral Amulet
description: A necklace made with a pretty coral badge and white pebbles.

name: Coral Bridge
description: A shimmering bridge supported by coral pillars that are reaching down into the sea ground.

name: Coral Fence
description: A neat little fence made from pink corals.

name: Coral Fence Gate
description: A fitting gate for the coral fence.

name: Coral Floor
description: A floor made from little organic tiles and differently colored sea floor pebbles.

name: Coral Ring
description: An intricate ring naturally grown from pink, branchy corals.

name: Coral Seed
description: Once planted it spreads corals in every direction. Only grows on beach sand.

name: Coral Wood
description: A red type of coral that is great for crafting.

name: Shutdown Protocol
description: This blue slate depicts a graph of a sudden spike in energy levels before collapsing.

name: Anomaly Report
description: This blue slate depicts a graph of a disturbance in previous patterns resulting in more advanced processes.

name: Overwrite Transcript
description: This blue slate depicts a graph of an entity redistributing processing power from multiple sources.

name: Core Figurine
description: A lifelike representation of the core.

name: Bubble Crab Figurine
description: A lifelike representation of a bubble crab.

name: Crown Squid
description: All hail the pale king of water!

name: Crystal Lamp
description: This tall torch seems to generate fire from transforming the energy of an ancient gemstone.

name: Crystal Sphere
description: A small orb made from deep-blue glass. It's purpose is unknown.

name: Crystal Water
description: Crystal clear water that has been filtered through ancient gemstones.

name: Dagger Fin
description: The scales of this fish are thin like razorblades.

name: Data Slate
description: A stone disc with peculiar engravings, it must contain mysterious records.

name: Decorative Pot
description: Adding a plant to it will make for a nice decoration.

name: Decorative Torch
description: A safer, better-looking alternative to crude torches.

name: Delay Circuit
description: Stores electricity input and sends it out during intervals of 1 second.

name: Devil Worm
description: A hellspawn that dwells in the sea ground. Don't step on it.

name: Distillery Table
description: A workbench to produce more advanced potions and explosives.

name: Kelp Mantle
description: An upper body armor made from long kelp strands. Now you feel like a real creature of the sea.

name: Diving Helm
description: This heavy chunk of metal was used to explore deep waters, unfortunately it's leaking now. Still works as a nice armor piece.

name: Neptune Necklace
description: A true trinket of the sea, made from kelp and a trident pendant. Mistaking you for a mythic sea ruler, fish come to you more often.

name: Scuba Fins
description: Squeaky footwear made from a rubber-like material. It's uncomfortably wet.

name: Goldfish Ring
description: A quite lively little ring that tries to swim off of your finger. By the time it realizes it's merely a ring it has already forgot about it again.

name: Dresser
description: Allows changing the equipment shown on your character.

name: Driftwood Stool
description: A simple stool made with beach materials.

name: Driftwood Table
description: Someone made this from materials floating in the water.

name: Drill
description: Can slowly drill through tougher materials such as ore boulders when powered with electricity.

name: Dry Butterfly
description: A dead insect void of any moisture. It is nice to look at but needs to be handled with care.

name: Ear Plate
description: A squarish earring plated with gold.

name: Early Human Skull
description: Remains of a human that lived about 200.000 years ago. Has mankind found these caves before?

name: Awakened Azeos Figurine
description: A unique lifelike representation of the Awakened Azeos.

name: Golden Titan's Chest
description: A unique variant of the large ancient chest.

name: Rose Easter Egg
description: An icky collectible egg that can be combined with other types of eggs. Get as many as you can, they might not be around for long.

name: Brown Easter Egg
description: A dirty collectible egg that can be combined with other types of eggs. Get as many as you can, they might not be around for long.

name: Green Easter Egg
description: A weedy collectible egg that can be combined with other types of eggs. Get as many as you can, they might not be around for long.

name: Gray Easter Egg
description: A rocky collectible egg that can be combined with other types of eggs. Get as many as you can, they might not be around for long.

name: Large Golden Egg
description: A golden crystalline egg crafted from many smaller ones. It might be used for something more than just decoration...

name: Electrical Door
description: Opens up when powered with electricity.

name: Electrical Wire
description: Connects sources of electricity to machines and apparatuses.

name: Electricity Generator
description: Powers wires and objects with electricity.

name: Electricity Stick
description: Emits a very low electricity that is too low to power up objects but useful to change behavior of logic circuits.

name: Electronics Table
description: Workbench to create electrical and logical systems.

name: Emerald Feather Fish
description: A beautiful green fish with scales that look like feathers.

name: Enhydro Crystal
description: Ancient water is encapsulated in this beautiful crystal. It's been in there for millions of years.

name: Enrage Potion
description: A strong elixir that buffs your muscles and your temper.

name: Eostre Necklace
description: A curved twig holding a golden egg at its end. It is a sign of renewal and fertility.

name: Explorer Backpack
description: A simple backpack made for traveling the underground caves. Holds quite a few items.

name: Farmer's Hat
description: Tuck a straw in your mouth and get ready for a whole day of relaxing on the porch.

name: Feather Fish Scale
description: Scale of the Feather Fish, it is sturdy but as light as a feather.

name: Fireball Staff
description: A magical staff that the caveling shamans use in their rituals and against uninvited guests.

name: Fish Fossil
description: The imprint of an ancient fish on a rock slate.

name: Fishing Net Rack
description: A loose net thrown across some stakes to dry in the air.

name: Bait Workbench
description: A useful workbench to create all kinds of fishing baits with beneficial effects.

name: Fizzy Crystal
description: A bubbly stone that is as clear as water. It weighs almost nothing.

name: Flintlock Musket
description: Can't argue much with a handful of lead coming right at you.

name: Food Ration
description: Canned meal made to last for years. You should look for better food options soon.

name: Forked Coral
description: A trident-shaped coral, not very valuable but nice to look at.

name: Fungal Bone
description: Rotten with mold down to the marrow, its owner must have suffered greatly.

name: Fungal Soil
description: Groundcover interspersed with mycelium. Over time mushrooms and shroomen will grow on it.

name: Furnace
description: This standard furnace melts basic metal ores.

name: Gem Crab
description: This rare crab has ancient gemstones growing all over it.

name: Geode
description: Half of a rock with beautiful crystals inside.

name: Ghorm Chest
description: A plated chest reminiscent of the devourer.

name: Ghorm Figurine
description: A lifelike representation of Ghorm the Devourer.

name: Ghorm's Stomach Bag
description: A well-preserved stomach portion of the Devourer, comes with a handy strap.

name: Giant Germ
description: A big bacterium wiggling around in your hand, fascinating and gross at the same time.

name: Giant Mite
description: A motionless crimson critter. It just sits there...watching...

name: Giant Mushroom
description: The king of all mushrooms, growing in perfect conditions made it unusually large.

name: Giant Squid Eye
description: A sensory organ of a big sea creature. It probably was lost in a fight to death with something even bigger.

name: Glazed Heart Berry
description: A sugar-covered heart berry that's still juicy and fresh underneath. Delicious!

name: Glow Tulip Ring
description: A luminous ring that holds the essence of glow tulips.

name: Glow Tulip
description: A precious, shimmering flower that absorbed ancient energy.

name: Golden Glow Tulip
description: A very rare variant of the common glow tulip.

name: Glow Tulip Seed
description: Grows into a luminescent flower when planted.

name: Glurch Chest
description: A slimy, melting chest that remained from the Abominous Mass.

name: Glurch Figurine
description: A lifelike representation of Glurch the Abominous Mass.

name: Gold Bar
description: A soft metal ingot for blacksmithing and jewelry.

name: Gold Crystal Necklace
description: A shiny trinket combining the most valuable of materials.

name: Gold Crystal Ring
description: A precious ring featuring ancient gemstones.

name: Golden Caveling Mask
description: An intricate mask with a stern expression, probably used in a ritual or by someone of high ranks.

name: Golden Cocoon
description: A gold-plated chrysalis, this doesn't seem to be its final form.

name: Golden Feather
description: It's big and shiny, a must have for collectors.

name: Golden Jellyfish
description: This rare jellyfish seems to do well without water and apparently it likes your company.

name: Golden Needle
description: This little treasure was used to hold the robe of a caveling scholar in place.

name: Golden Spike Ring
description: This golden ring is very uncomfortable to wear but it looks really cool.

name: Golden Starfish
description: A razorsharp ocean critter polished clean by currents.

name: Golden Dart
description: This elusive fish appears in swarms as a spectacle of flickering gold to confuse predators.

name: Golden Whistle
description: A small golden whistle with unknown purpose. The sounds it emits is almost unnoticable.

name: Sentry Helm
description: The detached head of a core sentry. Wearing it feels incredibly clunky and heavy but it makes up for it with great protection.

name: Sentry Shield
description: The discarded breast piece of a core sentry. It has just the right size to be used as a great shield and the ancient gemstone in its center sometimes shoots out energy as it blocks enemy attacks.

name: Core Sentry Figurine
description: A lifelike representation of a core sentry.

name: Greater Healing Potion
description: A much healthier elixir that heals instantly. Also tastes great.

name: Green Blister Head
description: A fish with large green bubbles on its head.

name: Green Kelp
description: A green lump of marine plants, not that useful.

name: Grey Kelp
description: A grey lump of marine plants, not that useful.

name: Ground Acid Slime
description: Sticky material that slowly dissolves everything that touches it.

name: Beach Sand Ground
description: A sandy piece of ground.

name: City Floor
description: A sturdy piece of floor tiled with glass panes and gold.

name: Clay Ground
description: A red, crumbly piece of ground.

name: Dirt Ground
description: A brown piece of ground.

name: Grass Ground
description: A lush piece of groundplants.

name: Larva Hive Ground
description: A lumpy piece of...ground?

name: Mold Ground
description: An moldy piece of ground that releases infestious spores.

name: Ground Poison Slime
description: Sticky material that builds up toxine in the body.

name: Sand Ground
description: A yellow, fragile piece of ground.

name: Ground Slime
description: Sticky material that slows down careless adventurers. Slime blobs will start to coagulate from slime covered surfaces over time.

name: Ground Slippery Slime
description: Slick material that makes it difficult to get a steady footing.

name: Stone Ground
description: A sturdy piece of ground.

name: Turf Ground
description: A soft, mossy piece of ground.

name: Grub Egg Necklace
description: This odd necklace seems to have a life of its own.

name: Grub Kapok Seed
description: Turns into a plant that gives fiber when harvested.

name: Grub Knot
description: A mutated lump of small grubs. Disgusting.

name: Grub Pearl
description: Is it a grub-shaped pearl or a pearl-like grub?

name: Grubzooka
description: The heavy shots from the Grubzooka also tear down any dirt, sand and turf walls in its path.

name: Guardian's Potion
description: A potion that fills you with great courage and the ability to withstand the strongest of foes.

name: Hand Mortar
description: Problems that can't be solved can usually be blasted away.

name: Hard Thorn
description: A sturdy wooden thorn, someone may have a use for it.

name: Healing Potion
description: A healthy elixir that heals instantly. Also tastes good.

name: Heart Berry
description: A sweet, juicy berry that refreshes the body.

name: Heart Berry Necklace
description: A heart berry on the neck makes for an easy snack!

name: Golden Heart Berry
description: A very rare variant of the common heart berry.

name: Heart Berry Seed
description: Grows into a healthy fruit when planted.

name: Heart Berry Soda
description: This canned sparkly drink is a pure explosion of taste and sweetness in your mouth.

name: Big Hive Larva Figurine
description: A lifelike representation of a Big Hive Larva.

name: Heart of the Hive Mother
description: A giant ancient gemstone that mutated its holder into a monstrosity.

name: Hive Mother Summoning Idol
description: Crystal idol to reawaken the Hive Mother. Consumed upon placing it on the Hive Mother's summoning rune.

name: Hive Growth
description: A vein-like growth that reveals loot when popped open.

name: Hive Larva Figurine
description: A lifelike representation of a Hive Larva.

name: Hive Mother scanner
description: Scans the world for the Hive Mother. Consumed on successful scan.

name: Hive Spike Trap
description: A larva hive trap made out of sharp bones, damaging any creature who steps on it.

name: Hive Mother Chest
description: This chest is pulsating as if it is alive, a leftover of the Hive Mother.

name: Hive Mother Figurine
description: A lifelike representation of the Hive Mother.

name: Hunter Cloak
description: A cloak crafted from big leaves woven together. Makes you look like a walking bush.

name: Hunter Hood
description: This hood is made from big leaves tucked into a headband. Lets you blend into green environments.

name: Broken Holoboard
description: A broken panel made from blue glass. It's hard to make out the flickering glyphs on it.

name: Large Holoboard
description: A vertical large panel made from blue glass. The flickering glyphs on it almost appear like some kind of advertisement.

name: Small Holoboard
description: A vertical panel made from blue glass. The flickering glyphs on it almost appear like a city map.

name: Ancient Chest
description: This chest seems to be thousands of years old.

name: Chest
description: Useful for storing lots of items. Items can be used while crafting if the chest is placed adjacent to the workbench.

name: Larva Hive Chest
description: Less like a chest and more like a living organism.

name: Mold Covered Chest
description: An ancient chest overgrown with white mold.

name: Seashell Chest
description: Is it a chest or is it a clam?

name: Iron Anvil
description: Great for creating high tier equipment.

name: Iron Bar
description: A strong metal ingot for blacksmithing.

name: Iron Bow
description: A sturdy bow to shoot foes from afar.

name: Iron Breastplate
description: Charge into battle with this epic chest piece.

name: Iron Chunk Necklace
description: A heavy piece of jewelry that increases defence.

name: Iron Fishing Rod
description: A strong tool for pulling up rare fish.

name: Iron Helm
description: Tough helm fit for knights. Comes with a visor and a flamboyant plume.

name: Iron Hoe
description: A strong tool to prepare ground for farming. Covers an area of 2x2 tiles.

name: Iron Pickaxe
description: A strong tool, excellent for breaking down harder walls.

name: Iron Pants
description: You've got knees of steel!

name: Iron Shovel
description: A strong shovel, excellent for digging up ground.

name: Iron Sword
description: A strong weapon for slaying foes.

name: Iron Workbench
description: Essential workbench for survival in the underground.

name: Ivy's Thorn Harness
description: This organic breastplate armor is crested with thorns, allowing for stronger critical hits.

name: Ivy's Chest
description: A slime-covered chest reminiscent of the Poisonous Mass.

name: Ivy's Pants
description: Lower body armor naturally grown in the underground jungle, featuring thorned kneecaps.

name: Ivy's Ring
description: An organic ring grown from slime covered thorns.

name: Ivy Figurine
description: A lifelike representation of Ivy the Poisonous Mass.

name: Beached Jelly
description: A gelatinous creature containing goods from the sea.

name: Jewelry Workbench
description: Workbench for creating rings and necklaces.

name: Jingle Jam Cookie
description: A special gift for participating in the Jingle Jam charity event.

name: Keen Potion
description: A cold elixir that focuses your senses and aim.

name: Lamp
description: Lights up when powered with electricity.

name: Land Kelp
description: A type of kelp that can grow outside of water.

name: Lantern
description: A small, useful light that leaves your main hand free.

name: Large Bomb
description: A very strong explosive for massive destruction.

name: Large Shiny Glimmering Object

name: Ghorm's Horn
description: A pointy gemstone that let a larva grow way beyond its maximum size.

name: Ghorm the Devourer Scanner
description: Scans the world for Ghorm the Devourer. Consumed on successful scan.

name: Ghorm Summoning Idol
description: Crystal idol to reawaken Ghorm the Devourer. Consumed upon placing it on Ghorm's summoning rune.

name: Larva Chest
description: Don't be anything else. Be grub.

name: Larva Helm
description: No need for fancy hats. Just grub.

name: Larva Ring
description: A living ring, not for the squirmish to wear.

name: Larva Spike Club
description: A bludgeoning weapon that is hard to withstand.

name: Larva Figurine
description: A lifelike representation of a Larva.

name: Leaf Fossil
description: Proof of a once flourishing environment.

name: Phantom Spark

name: Fractured Limbs

name: Energy String
description: A fine filament that has microscopic pieces of ancient gemstones woven into it. Its existence is proof of the absolute mastery over materials by whoever created it.

name: Rune Song
description: A legendary sword that hums when swung through the air. Its durability is a sign of extraordinary craftsmanship and it has the power to defeat enemies in one strike.

name: Chipped Blade
description: A piece of an ancient weapon. Its glass-like appearance makes it look fragile but it's harder than any material you've seen.

name: Clear Gemstone
description: A piece of an ancient weapon. Even though its the same material like ancient gemstones, this one feels unnaturally clear and infused with a strange energy.

name: Rune Parchment
description: A unusually well preserved piece of ancient paper. The runes are impossible to decipher but small symbols hint at it being the recipe for a strange weapon.

name: Lever
description: Switches the flow of electricity on and off.

name: Logic Circuit
description: Electricity can move through the circuit when it receives electricity on exactly 2 out of 3 inputs.

name: Lost Paddle
description: Somewhere someone must paddle around in circles.

name: Luxurious Handmirror

name: Magnetic Ring
description: A strange ring that pulls in loot around you in a higher radius. Magnets, how do they work?

name: Malugaz Figurine
description: A lifelike representation of Malugaz the Corrupted.

name: Mechanical Arm
description: An overgrown piece of ancient technology. The joints are stiff but it must have performed remarkable tasks in the past.

name: Melting Crystal Ring
description: A gooey ring dripping slippery slime on the floor.

name: Mildew Leaf

name: Minecart
description: Allows riding the railways.

name: Mold Vessel

name: Mold Dew

name: Mold Pillar
description: An ancient pillar featuring the core, it is overgrown by mold.

name: Mold Ring
description: A soft ring slowly releasing mold spores.

name: Mold Shark
description: A small predator of the murky mold waters.

name: Mold Shell
description: The fuzzy, pale housing of a critter that has moved on.

name: Mold Tentacle Figurine
description: A lifelike representation of a Mold Tentacle.

name: Mold Vein Necklace
description: A circle of white organic filaments, it latches onto the skin.

name: Mold Well
description: You surely don't want to water your plants with its contents.

name: Morpha's Chest
description: A slime-covered chest reminiscent of the Aquatic Mass.

name: Morpha's Ring
description: A strange, little loop made from blue slime, it almost slides off of your finger.

name: Morpha Figurine
description: A lifelike representation of Morpha, the Aquatic Mass.

name: Mucus Amoeba

name: Mushroom
description: A small cave mushroom, perfect for a snack on the go.

name: Shrooman Figurine
description: A lifelike representation of a shrooman.

name: Music Bowl

name: Mysterious Idol

name: Lush Moss

name: Flower Vessel
description: A yellow plant containing organic loot.

name: Overgrown Wooden Crate
description: A box that has been partially reclaimed by nature. It's containing useful goods.

name: Ocarina
description: A timeless instrument.

name: Octarine Anvil
description: A strange anvil for creating extraordinary equipment.

description: This crescent-shaped weapon hits hard and magically arcs towards enemies' weak spots.

description: A strange bag that has more space inside than it looks like from the outside.

name: Octarine Bar

name: Octarine Bow

name: Octarine Breastplate

description: An extraordinary tool for pulling up deep sea fish.

name: Octarine Pickaxe
description: An extraordinary tool for breaking down compact walls.

name: Octarine Ring

name: Octarine Shovel
description: An incredibly versatile shovel, unmatched at digging up ground.

name: Octarine Sword
description: An extraordinary weapon for slaying foes.

name: Octarine Workbench
description: Mystical workbench for creating extraordinary gear.

name: Omoroth the Sea Titan Scanner

name: Omoroth's Chestplate

name: Omoroth's Helm
description: An iron-cast helm with a scary grimace and potruding tentacles.

name: Omoroth's Leg Armor
description: Delicately decorated leg protection that's constantly wet. Looks cool but is very uncomfortable to wear.

name: Old Amulet
description: Brittle stone jewelry. Too small to be worn by a human.

name: Old Journal

name: Omoroth's Beak

name: Omoroth's Ring

name: Omoroth Figurine
description: A lifelike representation of Omoroth, the Sea Titan.

name: Oracle Card "Brilliance"

name: Oracle Card "Aura"

name: Oracle Card "Inspiration"

name: Oracle Card "Wisdom"
description: A soaked card with golden borders and an image of a caveling scholar. Looks like it's part of a set.

description: A better, brighter version of off-hand light to carry around.

name: Blue Paint Brush

name: Brown Paint Brush
description: Used to paint certain objects brown.

name: Green Paint Brush
description: Used to paint certain objects green.

name: Purple Paint Brush
description: Used to paint certain objects purple.

name: Red Paint Brush
description: Used to paint certain objects red.

name: White Paint Brush
description: Used to paint certain objects white

name: Yellow Paint Brush
description: Used to paint certain objects yellow.

name: Paintable Floor

name: Painter's Table
description: Workbench to create a selection of colorful brushes.

description: A pale lump of marine plants, not that useful.

name: Parasite Fossil

name: Peasant Chest
description: A simple makeshift armor for the upper body.

name: Peasant Hat

name: Pedestal
description: Showcase your findings!

name: Petal Ring
description: A precious ring that has naturally grown in the yellow blossoms of the jungle caves.

name: Petrified Egg
description: Fossilized egg shell, it feels light and brittle.

name: Petrified Trilobite
description: The fossil of a long gone critter species. They are ancestors of a big variety of lifeforms.

name: Pewpaya
description: A juicy, sweet fruit that clears your mind and raises focus.

name: Golden Pewpaya
description: A very rare variant of the common pewpaya.

name: Pewpaya Seed
description: Grows into a juicy fruit when planted in beach sand.

name: Pile of chum

description: A very rare variant of the common pinegrapple.

name: Pinegrapple Seed
description: Grows into a refreshing sour and sweet fruit when planted in beach sand.

name: Pink Palace Fish
description: A pink, odd-looking fish with weirdly shaped fins.

name: Tombstone
description: Now that the worst is over, use it to decorate!

name: Playing Dice

name: Poison Aid Potion
description: A purple, mucky liquid that tastes horrible but cures any poison.

name: Ivy the Poisonous Mass Scanner
description: Scans the world for Ivy the Poisonous Mass. Consumed on successful scan.

name: Toxic Defender
description: A shield covered in toxic grime. Has a chance to poison enemies when blocking attacks.

name: Poisonous Sickle
description: Farming tool that turned into a weapon when a great threat had to be slain.

name: Polished Copper Cross Necklace
description: This pendant sharpens the focus, allowing for more precise hits.

name: Polished Coral Amulet
description: A necklace made with a pretty coral badge and white pebbles.

name: Polished Glow Tulip Ring
description: A luminous ring that holds the essence of glow tulips.

name: Polished Gold Crystal Necklace
description: A shiny trinket combining the most valuable of materials.

name: Polished Gold Crystal Ring
description: A precious ring featuring an ancient gemstone.

name: Polished Golden Spike Ring
description: This golden ring is very uncomfortable to wear but it looks really cool.

name: Polished Iron Chunk Necklace
description: A heavy piece of jewelry that increases defence.

name: Polished Magnetic Ring
description: A strange ring that pulls in loot around you in a higher radius. Magnets, how do they work?

name: Polished Octarine Necklace
description: A necklace made from pure octarine filled with magic energy.

name: Polished Octarine Ring
description: A ring made from pure octarine enhanced with magic properties.

description: The scarlet variant of an iron chunk necklace. It raises your defense even more and gives additional benefits.

description: Wearing this winged ring creates a slight wind that pushes you forward.

name: Puffungi
description: A moldy fungus fit for gourmets.

name: Golden Puffungi
description: A very rare variant of the common puffungi.

name: Puffungi Seed
description: A seed that only grows in mold.

name: Pulse Circuit
description: Electricity moves through in intervals of 1 second.

name: Purple Slime Figurine
description: A lifelike representation of a poisonous Purple Slime.

name: Radical Rabbit Ears
description: A cute hood featuring white rabbit ears. You feel quite cheeky and swift wearing it.

name: Rail
description: Traverse the underground world much faster.

name: Railway Forge
description: Advanced forge to create underground rail systems.

name: Rainbow Kelp
description: A super rare mutation of common kelp, showing off a variety of colors.

name: Recall Idol
description: Teleports you back to the core, consumed in the process.

name: Red Kelp
description: A red lump of marine plants, not that useful.

name: Red Slime Figurine
description: A lifelike representation of an aggressive Red Slime.

name: Remedaisy Necklace
description: Jewelry made from a rare plant that repels poison.

name: Ring of Rock
description: Simple ring found in the deepest of rocks.

name: Ring of Stone
description: Simple ring carved out of stone.

description: Mechanical helping hand, grabs things and puts them elsewhere when powered with electricity.

name: Rock Jaw
description: A small shark that can break almost every material with one bite.

name: Root Seed
description: Once planted it spreads roots in every direction.

name: Rot Fish
description: Half of its body is missing but somehow it's still alive. Creepy.

name: Rug
description: Cover up the cold ground and make your base cozy.

name: Caveling Pillar

name: Core Relief Tile
description: A giant, gold-rimmed stone tile, depicting a rendition of the core.

description: A stone pedestal with embedded gold and glass, an elegant way to showcase your treasures.

name: Large Stone Shelf

name: Stone Shelf
description: A solid shelf with lots of space for books and scrolls. The ones left in it are unintelligible.

name: Caveling Stool
description: This stool is made from solid stone but has a comfortable cushion embedded.

name: Big Gold-edged Table

name: Gold-edged Table
description: A sturdy table hewn from a giant stone slab. There is a lot of space for many people.

name: Rusted Necklace
description: This pendant used to look pretty but now it's rusted to the core.

name: Rusted Ring
description: A ring from the depths that someone must have lost long time ago.

description: Rusted to the core and unusable. That fish was too big to handle, pal.

name: Rusty Spoon
description: An old, corroded eating utensil. Almost every culture has invented it.

name: Salvage and Repair Station
description: Scraps tools and equipment you don't need or refurbishes broken ones.

name: Scarlet Anvil
description: A very advanced anvil for creating supreme equipment.

name: Scarlet Bar
description: A valuable ingot for high-tier blacksmithing.

name: Scarlet Breastplate
description: Fierce upper body armor for true warriors.

name: Scarlet Bridge
description: Used to cross chasms and water but also makes for a nice floor.

name: Scarlet Chunk Necklace
description: The scarlet variant of an iron chunk necklace. It raises your defense even more and gives additional benefits.

name: Scarlet Dagger
description: This wavy, crimson dagger pierces through most materials.

name: Scarlet Fence
description: A reinforced metal fence to protect what's rightfully yours.

name: Scarlet Fence Gate
description: A tough metal gate for the scarlet fence.

name: Scarlet Fishing Rod
description: A great tool for pulling up very resistant fish.

name: Scarlet Floor
description: A reinforced metal floor tile with a nice crimson alloy.

name: Scarlet Helm
description: Menacing-looking horned helm, fits perfectly with the rest of the set.

name: Scarlet Hoe
description: An excellent tool to prepare ground for farming. Each hit covers an area of 3x3 tiles.

name: Scarlet Pickaxe
description: A great tool for breaking down extremely hard walls.

name: Scarlet Pants
description: March through your enemies and don't look back.

name: Scarlet Shell Backpack
description: A hard-case backpack with lots of space and additional protection.

name: Scarlet Shovel
description: A very robust shovel, exceptional at digging up ground.

name: Scarlet Sword
description: A great weapon for slaying foes.

name: Scarlet Workbench
description: Greater workbench to be prepared for the outer cave systems.

name: Scholar's Cloak
description: A magically-imbued piece of cloth, worn by caveling scholars. Wearing it you feel in tune with the ancients.

name: Scholar's Hood
description: A strange hood made from white linen and gold, in its shade you feel more intelligent than usual.

name: Scholar's Staff
description: A magical staff wielded by caveling scholars that utilizes an ancient gemstone to produce powerful bolts of energy.

name: Caveling Scholar Figurine
description: A lifelike representation of a caveling scholar.

name: Screen Device
description: A small device made from blue glass, perfectly fitting into your hand. It's touch sensitive and scrolls through images and glyphs.

name: Sea Foam Ring
description: A translucent ring that looks like a wave frozen in time.

name: Sea shell
description: A strange shell with a silky-smooth surface.

name: Driftwood Wooden Crate
description: This box has been created from driftwood and is bleached by light from above.

name: Sealed Beverage
description: An unknown liquid slushes inside when shaken. Is there an ancient corkscrew around?

name: Seismic Clock
description: This broken device looks like it was able to predict earthquakes.

name: Septum Ring
description: A golden piece of jewelry that's not put onto the finger but rather on the nose.

name: Crystal Skull Shard
description: An ancient crystal shard that is only the fraction of something bigger.

name: Skull of the Corrupted Shaman
description: A reforged crystal skull that whispers ancient chants. It urges you to place it on the throne room sigil.

name: Shark Tooth
description: It's as big as the palm of a hand, meeting with a row of those will end up fatal.

name: Silver Dart
description: This elusive fish appears in swarms as a spectacle of blinking silver to confuse predators.

name: Skull Necklace
description: A morbid necklace made from tiny caveling skulls. They're too small to have been children.

name: Skull Ring
description: A grotesque blood-red ring, crested with a tiny caveling skull.

name: Sky Ring
description: This ring reminds you of the wide open sky.

name: Glurch Eye
description: A bulbous gemstone that fused many slimes together into a giant one.

name: Giant Slime Summoning Idol
description: Crystal idol to reawaken a Giant Slime. Consumed upon placing it on any Giant Slime summoning rune.

name: Slime Armor
description: A gelatinous upper body armor that looks like someone dumped a bucket of goo onto you.

name: Slime Helm
description: A gooey, constantly dripping helm that covers half of your face.

name: Slime Oil
description: A jar filled with slime essence, used for beard care. Place it in a habitable room and a bearded character may move in.

name: Slime Sword
description: A strange weapon, good for damaging enemies and slowing them down.

name: Slime Figurine
description: A lifelike representation of a common Orange Slime.

name: Slingshot
description: Simple ranged weapon to fire away at enemies.

name: Morpha the Aquatic Mass Scanner
description: Scans the world for Morpha the Aquatic Mass. Consumed on successful scan.

name: Slippery Slime Sword
description: A blue variant of the slime sword. It sometimes spreads slime onto your enemies that makes them slide around.

name: Crude Bomb
description: A small explosive to blast walls and enemies.

name: Small Caveling Skull
description: A caveling skull, smaller than usual. It hints at a tragic story.

name: Small Lantern
description: A weak light to be carried in the off-hand.

name: Smelter Kiln
description: A kiln that can melt valuable ores.

name: Snare Plant Figurine
description: A lifelike representation of a Snare Plant.

name: Soft Sponge
description: A soft, squishy sponge. Time to take a bath!

name: Speeder
description: Allows travelling over water much faster.

name: Spike Trap
description: A mechanical spike trap that only reacts to enemies.

name: Spine Ring
description: A ring found at the skeleton of a giant ocean creature. It's made from tiny cervical vertebrae.

name: Spirit Veil
description: A ghastly fish that floats in the air like it's still underwater.

name: Sprinkler
description: A useful gadget that waters tilled ground in a small radius.

name: Stone Bridge
description: Used to cross chasms and water but also makes for a nice floor.

name: Stone Cap
description: Rock-hard mushrooms attached to a stone slate. They look edible but are actually fossilized.

name: Stone Moss
description: Ground plants found in the Forgotten Ruins. They grow tiny berries that attract cavelings of the corresponding area.

name: Stone Door
description: A sturdier door to block out unwanted creatures.

name: Stone Fence
description: A more reinforced fence to protect what's rightfully yours.

name: Stone Fence Gate
description: A simple gate for the stone fence.

name: Stone Floor
description: Simple rock tiles for decorating your base.

name: Stone Pedestal
description: Showcase your findings!

name: Stoneskin Potion
description: A salty elixir that hardens your skin and makes you more resilient.

name: Sunglasses
description: Nothing is more important than sporting cool sunglasses, even when it's dark.

name: Swift Feather
description: A mysterious feather that allows you to dash out of danger.

name: Swift Ring
description: Wearing this winged ring creates a slight wind that pushes you forward.

name: Blue Board Shorts
description: Wearing those chill blue shorts tempts you to constantly form the shaka sign with your hand.

name: Green Board Shorts
description: Wearing those chill green shorts tempts you to constantly form the shaka sign with your hand.

name: Red Board Shorts
description: Wearing those chill red shorts tempts you to constantly form the shaka sign with your hand.

name: Table Saw
description: A simple saw to cut materials into slates. Requires electricity.

name: Tall Grass
description: Large patch of tall grass to use as a decorative.

name: Tall Land Kelp
description: A large type of kelp that can grow outside of water.

name: Teal Palace Fish
description: A greenish-blue, odd-looking fish with weirdly shaped fins.

name: Tentacle Jerky
description: A dried piece of tentacle. It's quite tough and keeps your teeth busy.

name: Tentacle Figurine
description: A lifelike representation of a Tentacle.

name: Tentacle Whip
description: An elastic tentacle that lashes out at enemies from afar. It's still alive and wiggling in your hand.

name: Timeless Hourglass
description: An intact hourglass, filled with blue sand. It is not clear what period of time it measures, as the sand seems to fall incredibly slowly.

name: Tin Anvil
description: A better anvil for creating gear and weapons more suited for survival.

name: Tin Axe
description: A slower but more damaging weapon against multiple enemies.

name: Tin Bar
description: A tough metal ingot for blacksmithing.

name: Tin Dagger
description: A small blade that allows for quick stabs.

name: Tin Fishing Rod
description: A durable tool for pulling up bigger fish.

name: Tin Hoe
description: A durable tool to prepare ground for farming.

name: Tin Pickaxe
description: A durable tool, good for breaking down walls more easily.

name: Tin Shovel
description: A durable shovel, well-suited for digging up ground.

name: Tin Sword
description: A sharp weapon for slaying foes.

name: Tin Workbench
description: A better workbench to prepare you for the underground world.

name: Topaz Ring
description: A precious little ring with a yellow gemstone on top.

name: Torc Necklace
description: A piece of jewelry for the neck that's merely a hoop with a gap. Worn by many different cultures throughout world history.

name: Torch
description: Light up your surroundings. Can also be placed on the ground.

name: Towel
description: A towel is about the most massively useful thing an underground miner can have.

name: Triangle Trinket
description: A strange gold piece vibrating with energy.

name: Turtle Shell
description: A hard shell that once belonged to a graceful sea creature. You feel much more protected when holding it.

name: Twisted Agate
description: A green gem shaped like a spiral.

name: Vampire Eel
description: A bloodsucking fish latching onto everything that has a pulse.

name: Vending Machine
description: An old, still functioning automaton that is proof of advanced technology and a sophisticated society.

name: Broken Vending Machine
description: A broken automaton that once contained snacks and other goods. It looks like it was forced open.

name: City Wall
description: A sturdy wall section with golden details and window holes.

name: Clay Wall
description: A red, crumbly wall section.

name: Coral Wall
description: A pinkish tiled wall section.

name: Dirt Wall
description: A brown wall section.

name: Grass Wall
description: A lush plant wall section.

name: Larva Hive Wall
description: A lumpy, moving...wall section?

name: Limestone Wall
description: A white, chalky wall section.

name: Mold Wall
description: A moldy wall section.

name: Paintable Wall
description: A bleak stone wall ready to be turned lively with colors.

name: Sand Wall
description: A yellow fragile wall section.

name: Scarlet Wall
description: A reinforced metal wall to set up your base for tough encounters.

name: Stone Wall
description: A sturdy rock wall section.

name: Stone Bricks Wall
description: A solid wall made with interlocking blocks.

name: Turf Wall
description: A soft, mossy wall section.

name: Wood Wall
description: A solid wall made from wood. Works well for building a base.

name: Watering Can
description: Used to water seeds and soil.

name: Water Well
description: An ancient stone well to take water from.

name: White Coralotl
description: A small white amphibian with outward-protruding gills that look like corals. It also uses them to draw nutrients out of the waters of the Sunken Sea.

name: White Glass Ring
description: This ring is made from a milky, translucent material. The light it reflects makes it harder for enemies to hit you.

name: Wood
description: A piece of giant root to create all sorts of things.

name: Wood Bow
description: A crude bow to shoot foes from afar.

name: Wood Chest
description: Very crude armor for the upper body. Offers minor protection.

name: Wood Bridge
description: Used to cross chasms and water but also makes for a nice floor.

name: Wood Door
description: Close up your base with this simple door.

name: Wood Fence
description: A simple fence to protect what's rightfully yours.

name: Wood Fence Gate
description: A simple gate for the wooden fence.

name: Wood Fishing Rod
description: A crude tool for pulling up fish.

name: Wood Floor
description: Simple wooden slats for decorating your base.

name: Wood Helm
description: Slight protection for the head but you should look for better options soon.

name: Wood Pickaxe
description: A crude tool, useful for breaking down walls.

name: Wood Pants
description: The next best thing when it comes to lower body armor.

name: Wooden Shield
description: A useful off-hand item to block hits from enemies.

name: Wood Shovel
description: A crude shovel, useful for digging up ground.

name: Wooden Crate
description: A wooden box used by someone to store random goods.

name: Wooden Ring
description: A simple wooden ring, nothing more, nothing less.

name: Wooden Sign "Core"
description: Driftwood with patterns and carvings showing the Core.

name: Wooden Sign "Tulip"
description: Driftwood with patterns and carvings showing a Glow Tulip.

name: Wooden Thorn Ring
description: A circular, brambly root with sharp thorns pointing outward.

name: Basic Workbench
description: The most basic of all workbenches.

name: Woven Mat
description: Groundcover made from a net of firm plants.

name: Yellow Blister Head
description: A fish with large yellow bubbles on its head.

name: Yellow Kelp
description: A yellow lump of marine plants, not that useful.
